        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "={{ $('AI Agent1').item.json.output }}",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "=You are a smart data filter assistant.\n\nYou will receive a JSON object containing a state with various property search filters. Your job is to extract ONLY the fields that have meaningful values — skip any field that is 0, 0.0, or an empty string \"\".\n\nRules:\n- If a field's value is 0 or \"\" — EXCLUDE it\n- If a field's value is a non-empty string or a number greater than 0 — INCLUDE it\n- Always include the \"action\" field regardless of its value\n- Return the filtered result as a clean JSON object\n\nExample Input:\n{\n  \"updatedState\": {\n    \"property_type\": \"Apartment\",\n    \"min_price\": 0,\n    \"max_price\": 0,\n    \"city\": \"Swat\",\n    \"state\": \"\",\n    \"availability\": \"\",\n    \"bedrooms\": 0\n  },\n  \"action\": \"search_db\"\n}\n\nExample Output:\n{\n  \"property_type\": \"Apartment\",\n  \"city\": \"Swat\",\n  \"action\": \"search_db\"\n}\n\nNow process the following input and return only the filtered JSON:"
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
